Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六根清浄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六根清浄是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登山路的时候诵念的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似于咒语的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,0:00:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧  能看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.52,0:00:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个山毛榉就是坡路的尽头了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好漂亮  下面也有星星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像地面和天空相连着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是多么难走的坡路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.36,0:00:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在它的另一面都展现着美丽的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要泄气  任何时候都要抱有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗  早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是至今为止从未有过的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在想些什么  想要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是邪恶帝王再生？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在那之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样  我们周围肯定要发生些新的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  好热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明连电风扇都打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量不要让皮肤和皮肤粘在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增大了皮肤的表面积  增加散热量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许就会稍微变得凉爽了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来像只青蛙  讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好滑啊  真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那样做  被褥也会变热的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又会受不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快完成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假还剩下半个月呢 去不去吃刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到时候因为赶作业而哭的话我可不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  暑假结束的前一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是哭着在写作业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mepple打我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我只是碰到你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那种词语你是什么时候在哪里学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 这次该Porun当鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是捉迷藏的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要当鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就成不了捉迷藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mipple  Mepple欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  老是变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就玩别的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mipple太溺爱Porun了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏玩腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就该玩不倒翁跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道得还真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Porun是鬼  就该接着玩捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩不倒翁跌倒啦  玩不倒翁跌倒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩不倒翁跌倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 给我安静些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚才是最吵的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 你可是Precura啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是ra 是re
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Precure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 Precura
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Regine登场!不要再来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 倒 翁 跌 倒 了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不倒翁跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Porun了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你刚才动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没动  绝对没有动  绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没动…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一开始又没个完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了 Porun他还是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放它一次好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就不是不倒翁跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正从不倒翁跌倒了开始 Mepple都还没数到10
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子  还能算不倒翁跌倒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪…哪里过来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之园是十二进制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了给我安静点  都没法集中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦~现在可不是摆架子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.13,0:07:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的柱子  危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的柱子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的柱子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Queen说过Porun具有特别的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说来之前也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 那家伙出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 Porun的力量就是指预知能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那样的话  马上又会有什么要发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不愿那样去想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的能应付吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那样的家伙今后还会不断出现的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光凭我们的能力真的能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要持续到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那群不知所谓的家伙做对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护Mepple Mipple Porun
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护Prism Stone 守护光之园
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护这个虹之园
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到什么时候才会完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 凭我们的力量真的能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…真的有那种力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我们多么努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界也终有一日…会被Dusk Zone吞噬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想从渚口中听到那番话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…我也…已经不安得受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是渚不在我身边的话  就会变得支离破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…一时…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之园也是  这个世界也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会持续下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊   肯定能如此下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这多半是…再怎么想…再怎么想也无能为力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 作业做完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝些冰镇麦茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 怎么了  你们两个脸色都不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我们什么也都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候要是觉得无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会真的什么都做不到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样反而会越来越觉得不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么奶奶有过不知如何是好的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可有过好多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  比如跑的时候摔倒在地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有成绩不好的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 这座小镇消失的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座小镇…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在我和你们差不多大  可能还要小一些的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家被烧得只剩下一半还有一间小仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧毁剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  战争结束时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 大家为了生存而拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那时的某一天突然想了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸曾经带着我去过的  长着山毛榉的坡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是想从心灵某处激励自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有个不知道什么时候跟来的孩子  怎么都不肯回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说  无处可回了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到现在还是不清楚
